Resource Profile: Medication Request

Defining URL:https://digitalware-klinic.github.io/fhir/indisa/StructureDefinition-ProfileMedicationRequestKlinic
Version:1.0
Name:ProfileMedicationRequestKlinic
Title:Medication Request
Status:Active as of 2021-03-04
Definition:

An order or request for both supply of the medication and the instructions for administration of the medication to a patient.

Publisher:DigitalWare S.A. - Klinic-HIS
Copyright:

Digitalware 2021 CC.

Source Resource:XML / JSON / Turtle

The official URL for this profile is: 

https://digitalware-klinic.github.io/fhir/indisa/StructureDefinition-ProfileMedicationRequestKlinic

IdPathDetailsRequirements
dom-2MedicationRequestIf the resource is contained in another resource, it SHALL NOT contain nested Resources
: contained.contained.empty()
dom-3MedicationRequestIf the resource is contained in another resource, it SHALL be referred to from elsewhere in the resource or SHALL refer to the containing resource
: contained.where((('#'+id in (%resource.descendants().reference | %resource.descendants().as(canonical) | %resource.descendants().as(uri) | %resource.descendants().as(url))) or descendants().where(reference = '#').exists() or descendants().where(as(canonical) = '#').exists() or descendants().where(as(canonical) = '#').exists()).not()).trace('unmatched', id).empty()
dom-4MedicationRequestIf a resource is contained in another resource, it SHALL NOT have a meta.versionId or a meta.lastUpdated
